Package: nift
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Modern C++ static site generator
 Nift is a static site generator that compiles content with templating,
 Lua scripting, and incremental rebuilds. v2 is a from-scratch C++23
 rewrite of the original Nift (nsm).
